nd on you.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5352, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 993 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5199,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/16\/best-sadaqah-tazkiyyah\/","url_meta":{"origin":26759,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Best charity is most difficult to give","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, which charity has the greatest reward?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThat you give charity while you are healthy, greedy, fearing poverty, and hoping to be rich. Do not delay\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17537,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/09\/tasbih-tahmid-33-times\/","url_meta":{"origin":26759,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Glorify Allah 33 times after every prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The poor emigrants came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, saying, \u201cThe wealthy have taken the highest degrees and blessed ranks!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHow is that?\u201d They said, \u201cThey pray as we pray, they fast as we fast, they give in\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11839,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/25\/permission-to-keep-gifts\/","url_meta":{"origin":26759,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Gifts: Take gifts to keep or give away in charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, gave me a gift and I said, \"Give it to someone poorer than me.\" The Prophet said, \"Take it and keep it or give it in charity. Whatever comes to you of this property, take it without extravagance\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4568,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/08\/neighbors-do-not-belittle-any-gift\/","url_meta":{"origin":26759,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Neighbors: Do not belittle any gift, no matter how small","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 8, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Muslim women, do not look down on any gift for your neighbor, even a sheep's hoof.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6017, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1030 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1758,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/12\/22\/plant-tree-reward-charity\/","url_meta":{"origin":26759,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Every tree a Muslim plants is rewarded as charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 22, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas bin Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo Muslim plants a tree or sows a seed and then a bird, or a human, or an animal eats from it but that it is charity for him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2320, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26759","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=26759"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href"